text:
Hi Everyone,

I have created a table using HubDB. But it's not updating the value in the Custom Module that I have created. I have checked the api and everything working fine there. Can anyone tell me what are the issues?

Here is the code I am using to get table data:

{% for row in hubdb_table_rows(dynamic_page_hubdb_table_id, 'all_topics=Customer Stories') %}

                &lt;div class="resources_col boxres box_topic all_to_pic all_indus_show res_tech_{{ row.tags_resources.id }}  all_indus_{{row.all_industries.id}}"&gt;
                   {% if row.image.url %}
                    &lt;a href="{{row.link}}"&gt;
                      &lt;img src="{{ row.image.url }}" width="500" {% if row.image.width &gt; row.image.height %}class="landscape" {% endif %}  alt="{{ row.name }} Headshot"&gt;
                    &lt;/a&gt;
                    {% endif %}
                  &lt;div class="locate"&gt;
                    &lt;div class="l-date"&gt;
                      &lt;span&gt;{{ row.tags_resources.name }}&lt;/span&gt;
                      &lt;h4 class="name_search"&gt;{{row.name}}&lt;/h4&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;div class="l-date date_published_press"&gt;
                      &lt;span&gt;Date&lt;/span&gt;
                      &lt;div class="date-published"&gt;
                        {{ row.date|datetimeformat('d/M/yyyy') }}
                      &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                    &lt;div class="reg-btn-list"&gt;
                      &lt;a href="{{row.link}}"&gt;Read More &lt;span&gt;&lt;img alt="arrow" src="<https://www.flosum.com/hubfs/arrow-red.png>"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;
                    &lt;/div&gt;
                  &lt;/div&gt;
                &lt;/div&gt;
                {% endfor %}
